@startuml akdb-database-facade
title AKDB - Database Facade
component "Services" as Services
component "connect / managed_connection" as Connection
component "Database facade" as Facade
component "SQL compatibility rewrites" as Rewrite
component "Migration runner" as Migrations
database "sqlite3" as SQLite
database "psycopg / PostgreSQL" as PG
Services --> Facade : execute, executescript, commit
Connection --> SQLite : AKDB_DATABASE_PATH
Connection --> PG : AKDB_DB_URL
Facade --> Rewrite : PostgreSQL only
Rewrite --> PG : qmark?pyformat, JSON extract rewrite
Facade --> SQLite : native SQL
Migrations --> Facade : ordered additive schemas
note bottom of Facade
Backend branching is confined to db/connection.py,
db/database.py, schema selection and documented service seams.
end note
@enduml
